                      <span class="text-xl font-bold text-text">$144.00</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1">
                      <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">School Zone Violation</span>
                      <span class="text-xl font-bold text-text">$169</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="text-xs text-amber-800 mt-2 font-medium">⚠ $144.00 court fee, paid on or before the appearance/plea date on the citation. NO DSC or Deferral allowed for SCHOOL ZONE or CONSTRUCTION ZONE violations (no exceptions). CDL holders are NOT eligible.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- How to Request -->
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-3">How to Request DSC Approval</p>
                  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
                    <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[10px] p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
                        <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="8" fill="#34C759" stroke="#34C759" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M6 9l2 2 4-4" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5">
                          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-text-body">In-person</span>
                          <span class="text-sm text-text-body">Submit a written plea + $144 + documents in person at 211 N. Sherman, Mexia, TX 76667. Pay in cash (exact amount — court does not make change), money order, cashier check, personal check, or card (cards add 3% fee).</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[10px] p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
                        <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="8" fill="#34C759" stroke="#34C759" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M6 9l2 2 4-4" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5">
                          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-text-body">Mail</span>
                          <span class="text-sm text-text-body">Mail a written plea + court fee + documents via money order, cashier check, or personal check (no temporary, third-party, non-local, or out-of-state checks; do NOT send cash) to 211 N. Sherman, Mexia, TX 76667.</span>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[10px] p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
                        <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="8" fill="#34C759" stroke="#34C759" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M6 9l2 2 4-4" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-0.5">
                          <span class="text-sm font-bold text-text-body">Online</span>
                          <span class="text-sm text-text-body">Pay online at cityofmexia.com via card (3% fee) or electronic check (3% fee). Note: the plea/DSC request itself must be made in writing.</span>
                          <a href="https://www.cityofmexia.com/196/Online-Payments" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-xs text-primary hover:underline break-all mt-0.5">www.cityofmexia.com/196/Online-Payments</a>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Required Documents -->
                <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[14px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-4">
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">To Request Approval — Submit These</p>
                    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Written plea of Guilty/No Contest requesting DSC (signed plea form)</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Copy of valid proof of insurance showing the violator as an insured/covered driver</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Copy of valid Texas Driver License (Regular Classified) OR proof of active military duty</span></li>
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>$144.00 court fee</span></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                  <div>
                    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-body uppercase tracking-wide mb-2">After Completing the Course — Submit These</p>
                    <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
                      <li class="text-sm text-text-body flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Driving Safety Course completion certificate (and a certified driving record if required by the court)</span></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Important Notes -->
                <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-[14px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-2">
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800">Important Deadlines &amp; Local Rules</p>
                  <ul class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 list-none m-0 p-0">
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Request deadline: Plea and DSC request must be made in writing on or before the appearance date shown on the citation; the $144 court fee, proof of insurance, and driver license copy must be submitted by that date.</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Completion window: Once the court approves the DSC request, the driver has 90 days to complete all requirements and submit all documents. NO due-date extensions allowed..</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Eligibility: must hold a valid Regular Classified TX Driver License (or proof of active military duty); DSC not taken in the past 12 months and not currently taking one for another violation; valid TX liability insurance in effect at the violation date showing you as a covered driver.</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Speeding eligibility: the cited speed must be less than 25 mph over the posted limit.</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>CDL holders are NOT eligible for DSC or Deferral.</span></li>
                    <li class="text-sm text-amber-900 flex items-start gap-2"><span class="mt-1 shrink-0">•</span><span>Age 17 and up only; juveniles 16 and under must appear before the judge with a parent or legal guardian.</span></li>
                  </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- Forms -->
                <div>
                  <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-text mb-3">Court Forms &amp; Resources</p>
                  <div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
                    <a href="https://www.cityofmexia.com/DocumentCenter/View/128/Court-Policies-and-Plea-Form-PDF" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[10px] p-4 flex items-center gap-3 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors group">
                      <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 text-primary" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10.5 2.25H5.25A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 3.75 3.75v10.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5 1.5h7.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 0 1.5-1.5V6.75L10.5 2.25z"/><polyline points="10.5 2.25 10.5 6.75 14.25 6.75"/></svg>
                      <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary group-hover:underline">Court Policies and Plea Form (PDF)</span>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Contact -->
                <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[14px] p-4 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                  <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1 sm:col-span-2">
                    <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Court Hours</span>
                    <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-text-body">Monday–Friday 8:00 AM – 4:00 PM (closed holidays and City closings)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1">
                    <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Phone</span>
                    <a href="tel:2545624181" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:underline">(254) 562-4181</a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1">
                    <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Email</span>
                    <a href="mailto:RachelR@cityofmexia.com" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:underline break-all">RachelR@cityofmexia.com</a>
                  </div>
                  <div class="bg-white rounded-[10px] p-4 flex flex-col gap-1 sm:col-span-2">
                    <span class="text-xs text-text-body font-medium uppercase tracking-wide">Website</span>
                    <a href="https://www.cityofmexia.com/177/Municipal-Court" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary hover:underline break-all">www.cityofmexia.com/177/Municipal-Court</a>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Always verify -->
                <div class="bg-surface-muted border border-border rounded-[14px] p-4 flex items-start gap-3">
                  <svg class="w-[18px] h-[18px] shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none"><circle cx="9" cy="9" r="8" fill="#0967d2" stroke="#0967d2" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M9 5v4M9 13h.01" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
                  <p class="text-sm text-text-body leading-relaxed">Always verify DSC requirements directly with Mexia Municipal Court before submitting anything. Court fees, deadlines, and procedures can change. Call <a href="tel:2545624181" class="text-primary hover:underline font-medium">(254) 562-4181</a> or visit <a href="https://www.cityofmexia.com/177/Municipal-Court" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">www.cityofmexia.com/177/Municipal-Court</a>.</p>
                </div>

                <p class="text-xs text-text-subtle text-right">Court information last verified: June 2026</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          )}

        </div><!-- /left col -->

        <!-- Right Column — Buy Box -->
        <div class="lg:w-[300px] flex-shrink-0">
